    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/ac4249995dd712942ba35004da857a87.poster.avif?t=1771257500\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/ac4249995dd712942ba35004da857a87.webm?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/ac4249995dd712942ba35004da857a87.mp4?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >神秘的诅咒笼罩大地……</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着一股魔法冲击波席卷大地，各种野生动物突然变成了可怕的怪物，开始和当地居民作对……集结队伍，掷出骰子，踏上穿越诸岛的激战之旅，将这诅咒彻底终结吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/2a5e24cf5c29489d0ca5a7c268e64c70.poster.avif?t=1771257500\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/2a5e24cf5c29489d0ca5a7c268e64c70.webm?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/2a5e24cf5c29489d0ca5a7c268e64c70.mp4?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走上终结神秘诅咒的征途，成为骰子大师和战术家吧！每次冒险开始前，你都将挑选 3 名能力和打法风格各不相同的英雄组成队伍，踏入荒野。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沿途营救新的英雄，获得改变构筑思路的强大物品，然后在刚刚拜你所赐免于厄运的小商店里把辛苦赚来的金币统统豪掷！每次决定、每个任务，都将帮助你的英雄以独特的方式不断成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/b2ceb0ac9d5e24832878373b8df3769a.poster.avif?t=1771257500\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/b2ceb0ac9d5e24832878373b8df3769a.webm?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/b2ceb0ac9d5e24832878373b8df3769a.mp4?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色将在自己回合开始时掷出骰子，然后利用掷出的点数来驱动各种行动。《Dobbel Dungeon》没有命中概率机制，相反，只要你有所需的骰子，你的行动就会按照描述精确执行，让你得以每回合精心规划掷骰结果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，如果你发现掷出的点数不尽如人意，也有办法通过操纵点数的物品和技能，“轻轻推动”一切朝着你所料想的方向发展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/5c1067de703998c6f2046e1429579746.poster.avif?t=1771257500\" width=1170 height=698 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/5c1067de703998c6f2046e1429579746.webm?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/5c1067de703998c6f2046e1429579746.mp4?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被敌人修理得太惨？需要更多骰子来驱动各种行动？或者，总差那么一步才能够到目标？那就搞点高品质道具来占得先机吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等一下，精彩不止于此！除了提升属性外，某些物品还附带有额外的行动、被动效果，甚至还能为你的技能带来变化！选择可谓应有尽有！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/057583ab7fe6bfb212f071494e30102d.poster.avif?t=1771257500\" width=1170 height=698 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/057583ab7fe6bfb212f071494e30102d.webm?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/057583ab7fe6bfb212f071494e30102d.mp4?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次完成任务和额外目标，你都会获得宝贵的技能点，可以用来点亮英雄的技能树。投入到英雄身上的点数越多，就能解锁越强大的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，技能点是共享资源，所以务必谨慎使用哦！哪怕构筑并不成功，也可以在下一次冒险中尝试全新的策略！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/93705d17bafce8ebebeba0beffd1c84c.poster.avif?t=1771257500\" width=612 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185680/extras/93705d17bafce8ebebeba0beffd1c84c.webm?t=1771257500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以上内容有没有引起你的兴趣呢？《Dobbel Dungeon》还在开发之中，未来我们还将揭秘更多游戏特色，务必将我们的游戏加入愿望单并关注本页面，第一时间获知最新情报！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试玩版限制：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 名可玩英雄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 件独特物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛屿地图仅限森林</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗生成多样性有限</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人阵营仅限猪头人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗环境仅限森林室外</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败第一个 Boss 后冒险即告结束</p></li></ul>",
